Hare (Hare/Hare)
Monster Rancher Metropolis: Monster Rancher EVO Archive (PS2): CD/DVD/Game List (North American Version ONLY): Hare: Hare (Hare/Hare)
Hare is the monster the game will make when the PS2 system cannot read a disc. This means that any and all GameCube games, XBox games, PC games (without separate music tracks), out of region DVDs, out of region PS2 games, any CD placed in the tray upside-down, and most burned CDs & DVDs will all make Hares.
Please do not post such discs here as separate entries, such posts will be deleted.
